Plot: As Eve begins writing songs as a way to sort through some emotional problems, she meets James and Cassie, two musicians each at crossroads of their own.
Title: God Help the Girl
Actors: Emily Browning, Olly Alexander, Hannah Murray, Pierre Boulanger
tomatoConsensus: While it may strike harder-hearted viewers as excessively twee, God Help the Girl floats by on its sweet charm and talented cast.
